  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Consolidation of Peace and Security between Farming and Herding Communities in the Provinces of Salamat, Sila and Ouadda&#xEF;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project contributes to the reduction of agro-pastoral tensions and conflicts in Eastern Chad through Transhumance Tracking Tool (TTT) activities, which are encompassed in three main components including the implementation of TTT&#x2019;s early warning system to inform prevention and management of conflict activities by reporting alerts on transhumance-related tensions and conflicts, the identification of transhumance movements patterns through the collection of data on transhumance flow and breeders&#x2019; profiles, and support the establishment or dynamization of local prevention and conflict management committees.</narrative>
  </description>
